about.summary: Useful property variants for Python programming (required properties, writable properties, cached properties, etc)

name: property-manager
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "property-manager" %}
{% set version = "3.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 93e76da9ae7af13cccc2cd1e3b47219950c56c125cd962aaed693894af267c54

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: '{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv '

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python

  run:
    - humanfriendly >=4.12
    - python
    - verboselogs >=1.1

test:
  imports:
    - property_manager

about:
  home: https://property-manager.readthedocs.org
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: Useful property variants for Python programming (required properties, writable properties, cached properties, etc)
  doc_url: https://property-manager.readthedocs.io/en/latest/
  dev_url: https://github.com/xolox/python-property-manager

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - rpetit3
